            {
                "name": "Maneuver in Flight",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "name": "Falling",
                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "When you fall more than 5 feet, you take falling damage when you land, which is bludgeoning damage equal to half the distance you fell. If you take any damage from a fall, you're knocked prone when you land. You can Grab an Edge as a reaction to reduce or eliminate the damage from some falls. More detailed rules for falling damage appear here.",
                        "sources": [
                            {
                                "type": "source",
                                "name": "Player Core",
                                "link": {
                                    "type": "link",
                                    "name": "Player Core pg. 233",
                                    "alt": "Player Core pg. 233",
                                    "game-obj": "Sources",
                                    "aonid": 216
                                },
                                "page": 233,
                                "errata": {
                                    "type": "link",
                                    "name": "2.0",
                                    "alt": "2.0",
                                    "game-obj": "Sources",
                                    "aonid": 216
                                }
                            }
                        ],
                        "links": [
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Grab an Edge",
                                "alt": "Grab an Edge",
                                "game-obj": "Actions",
                                "aonid": 2313
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "here",
                                "alt": "here",
                                "game-obj": "Rules",
                                "aonid": 2352
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                "text": "You try a difficult maneuver while flying. Attempt an Acrobatics check. The GM determines what maneuvers are possible, but they rarely allow you to move farther than your fly Speed.",
